<template>
    <el-form :inline="true" :model="newTopicForm" class="form_main">
        <el-form-item label="课题名称">
          <el-input v-model="newTopicForm.topicName"></el-input>
        </el-form-item>
        <el-form-item label="课题类型">
          <el-select v-model="newTopicForm.topictype" >
            <el-option label="设计" :value="0" ></el-option>
            <el-option label="论文" :value="1"></el-option>
          </el-select>
        </el-form-item>
        <el-form-item label="课题来源">
            <el-select v-model="newTopicForm.topicSource" >
              <el-option label="自命题" :value="0"></el-option>
              <el-option label="企业" :value="1"></el-option>
              <el-option label="教师科研" :value="2"></el-option>
            </el-select>
          </el-form-item>
        <el-form-item>
          <el-button type="primary" @click="onSubmit">新增毕设课题</el-button>
        </el-form-item>
      </el-form>

</template>

<script>
export default{
    name:"NewTopic",
    data(){
        return{
            newTopicForm:{
                topicName:"课题名称",
                topictype:1,
                topicSource:1
            }
        }
    }
}
</script>
<style scoped lang="less">
.form_main{
    line-height: 23px;
}
</style>
